ibute anthology, when talking with a literature professor a few weeks back. Glad that panned out, and some of the remarks in the essay have given me some ideas.<br /><br />","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"7 years ago","ctime":"July 17 2009, 22:22:15 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://hippoiathanatoi.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"hippoiathanatoi","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"hippoiathanatoi","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://hippoiathanatoi.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"hippoiathanatoi","ctime_ts":1247869335,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/95231.html?replyto=6539263","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/95231.html?thread=6539263#t6539263","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/95231.html?thread=6539263#t6539263","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/95231.html?thread=6539263#t6539263","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"keele864","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://keele864.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":6539263,"talkid":25543,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/95231.html?thread=6539263#t6539263","above":6526207,"upictitle":"keele864: pic#0","article":"Note that the article was written by a literature professor. I graduated from his school, so I wrote him an email saying I would have taken a class with him had I known there was a Vance fan in the department. ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"7 years ago","ctime":"July 19 2009, 17:56:25 UTC